t=\"#feedbackModal_main_8419693\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104epp1665702821950_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/epp1665702821950_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/epp1665702821950_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"epp1665702821950\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Match Brackets\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify whether Uniface should check for matching parentheses, braces, and brackets in this field.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"epp1665702821950__section_w2840ab1b5b1_w2841ab1b5_w2842ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"epp1665702821950__table_d11405e1_d11406e1_d11407e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"epp1665702821950__table_d11405e1_d11406e1_d11407e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"epp1665702821950__table_d11405e1_d11406e1_d11407e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"epp1665702821950__table_d11405e1_d11406e1_d11407e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"epp1665702821950__table_d11405e1_d11406e1_d11407e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets the <code class=\"ph codeph\">BRM</code> field syntax code, which requires brackets\n                           to be matched.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"epp1665702821950__table_d11405e1_d11406e1_d11407e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"epp1665702821950__table_d11405e1_d11406e1_d11407e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Uniface does not check for matching brackets.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"epp1665702821950__section_bhp_v4q_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d314826e124\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"epp1665702821950__p_d8126e1_d8127e1_d8128e1\">Uniface checks for an equal number of left and right\n            brackets and that they are in the correct order. The matched brackets include:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"epp1665702821950__ul_mwx_w4q_qwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epp1665702821950__li_d3884e1_d3885e1_d3886e1\">Parentheses: <code class=\"ph codeph\">( )</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epp1665702821950__li_d3887e1_d3888e1_d3889e1\">Braces: <code class=\"ph codeph\">{ }</code>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"epp1665702821950__li_d3890e1_d3891e1_d3892e1\">Brackets: <code class=\"ph codeph\">[ ]</code>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"epp1665702821950__section_vnd_x4q_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d314826e154\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"epp1665702821950__p_d99089e1_d99090e1_d99091e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zlt1665702557043.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zlt1665702557043.html\" title=\"The Field Syntax property specifies the input format for data, including the entry format (for example, 1-Dec-14 or 20141201), the allowed characters, and whether the field is mandatory or read-only.\">Field Syntax</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419693\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8419693\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Match Brackets Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Match Brackets Specify whether Uniface should check for matching parentheses, braces, and brackets in this field. Value Description True Sets the BRM field syntax code, which requires brackets to be matched. False Uniface does not check for matching brackets. Description Uniface checks for an equal number of left and right brackets and that they are in the correct order. The matched brackets include: Parentheses: ( ) Braces: { } Brackets: [ ] Applies To Field Syntax Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}